race.comment: MIXED SIGNALS (4) resumes here but the form she showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this calibre. Tuned up for this with two solid Warwick trials and can run a big race while fresh. The well-related ADMITTED (5) (half to G3 winner Heuristic) is another first-up but has a handy fresh record with two wins and a second from four attempts. Drawn to sit up on speed from the inside marble and will give backers a sight. FLAMING CONQUEST (1) is three from three around this circuit and gets a stack of weight relief with the 3kg claim. Include in calculations. CAMPAI (2) next in line.
